{"lemma":"مُشَيِّعِي","slug":"مُشَيِّعِي","root":"ش.#.ع","root_slug":"ش-_-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-_-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23538","n23541"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B4%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%90%D9%91%D8%B9%D9%90%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23538","headword_ar":"مَشِيعٌ","root":"$yE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Filled;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) applied to a vessel. (K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Very rancorous, malevolent, malicious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spiteful; filled with baseness, meanness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sordidness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA. [In the CK, erroneously said to be, in this sense,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$oyaE","text_ar":"مِشْيَع"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makoyal","text_ar":"مَكْيَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$iyE","text_ar":"مَشِيع"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"makiyl","text_ar":"مَكِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) Hence also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa Dab~N ma$iyEN","text_ar":"هُوَ ضَبٌّ مَشِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a lizard of the kind called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Db~","text_ar":"ضبّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very rancorous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (TA.) IAar says, I heard Abu-l-Mekárim revile a man, saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa xab~N ma$iyEN","text_ar":"هُوَ خَبٌّ مَشِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [perhaps correctly"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~N","text_ar":"ضَبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but see this word, which is used as a syn. sequent to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xab~N","text_ar":"خَبٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is like a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dab~","text_ar":"ضَبّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is very rancorous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and unprofitable;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$iyEN","text_ar":"مَشِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", here, being with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O;) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iEotuhu","text_ar":"شِعْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"“ I filled it. ” (O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n23541","headword_ar":"مُشَيَّعٌ","root":"$yE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Courageous:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, TA:) as though he were encouraged and emboldened and strengthened by another, or encouraged and emboldened by the strength of his heart: (O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whose heart is encouraged and emboldened by every formidable affair in which he has embarked."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-  And (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Very quick"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speedy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hasty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, Z, O, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almu$ay~aEapu","text_ar":"المُشَيَّعَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a trad. relating to sheep or goats to be slaughtered as victims on the day of sacrifice, in which trad. such are forbidden, (O, Msb, K,) means the sheep or goat (Mgh)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that requires one to urge it on after the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because of its weakness"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and leanness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because of its lack of strength to follow them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or, as some relate it, the word is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almu$ay~iEapu","text_ar":"المُشَيِّعَةُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, O, Msb, K,) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that ceases not to follow the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alganama","text_ar":"الغَنَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tazaAlu tu$ay~iEu","text_ar":"لَا تَزَالُ تُشَيِّعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", O, K, * i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tatobaEuhaA","text_ar":"تَتْبَعُهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", Mgh, O, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that ceases not to lag behind the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sheep"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not coming up with them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but always going behind them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because of its leanness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K;) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ay~aEa AlD~ayofa","text_ar":"شَيَّعَ الضَّيْفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. above (see 2)]; (Mgh;) or as though urging on the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"] sheep or goats. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Msb","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}